<br />
When i am tasked with pulling, i'll come to where I want the mob to be.  IF any group members have moved up a hair, which will cause the mob to path near the the player before it arrives where i want it to be, I can make sure it doesn't stop at that individual by sitting until the mob runs past them, then standing just before it reaches melee range.<br />
<br />
Oh, yeah, 8 to 12 seconds is a bit long for a grind group.  I usually ask for that, when I use seconds, in hopes of getting 5 seconds out of them.  Another way to approach is to tell them to wait till one heal lands before attacking / casting.</div>
