				People arent stupid, they are just lazy and dont like to have to think about what they are doing. If you have a problem with people dieing early or ruining raids by pulling aggro off the MT, dont accept it and make them responsible for figuring out what they are doing wrong.<br />
<br />
Anger Management Program<br />
<br />
If player_01 overaggros and dies early<br />
Then /tell player_01 &quot;You overaggrod. Dont do it again, this is a warning&quot;<br />
<br />
If player_01 overaggros and dies early again<br />
Then /tell player_01 &quot;You overaggrod yet again. If it happens again, your gonna be looking for another guild.&quot;<br />
